-- Irish Mortgage Lenders Want All Borrower Data, Post Reports
-- B y   C o l m   H e a t l e y
-- 2012-02-12T11:49:37Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-02-12/irish-mortgage-lenders-want-all-borrower-data-post-reports.html
Mortgage lenders in Ireland want
access to all financial information relating to borrowers in
order to help them manage potential loan arrears, the  Sunday
Business Post  reported today, without citing anyone.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Colm Heatley in Belfast at 
